

" Configure template mapping, in gvim <D-Space> triggers the <c-p>

" Jump between {{ var }} placeholders in Normal mode with <Ctrl-p>
nnoremap <D-Space> /{{\s*\l.\{-1,}\s*}}<cr>c/{{\s*\l*\s*}}/e<cr>

"Jump between {{ var }} placeholders in Insert mode with <Ctrl-p>
inoremap <D-Space> <ESC>/{{\s*\l.\{-1,}\s*}}<cr>c/{{\s*\l*\s*}}/e<cr>
